ast.name: Lisp for Touchdevelop
ast.comment:
**Lisp for Touchdevelop** is a short implementation of the Lisp programming language written in Touchdevelop, bundled with a code editor. Running the app will bring up the code editor, along with several examples. Please note: I coded this in only two days, so expect some roughness. Specifically, there is absolutely NO error handling: if you type incorrect code, it will crash the program. For more information, see my [blog](http://michael0x2a.com/blog/lisp-for-touchdown)

Hashtag goodness!

#mshs2013
